		Testing web page efficiency
			Browser controls -
				refresh page(using cache if available): Ctrl + R
				refresh page (ignoring cache) - Ctrl + Shift + R
			http://www.webpagetest.org/
			https://plus.google.com/+NatDuca/posts?e=-RedirectToSandbox
			https://code.google.com/p/skia/
			http://stevesouders.com/cuzillion/
			http://aerotwist.com/blog/dont-guess-it-test-it/

			Strategy to Minimize total bytes, minimize # of critical resources
			(eg. files in Critical Rendering Path), shorten CRP length (# of roundtrips
			 between browswer and server needed to render page)
				Techniques for HTML, CSS, JavaScript
					Minify, Compress, Cache
				Techniques unique to CSS
					Minimize use of render blocking resources via
						1. Use of media queries on <link> to unblock rendering
						2. Use Inline CSS
				Techniques unique to JavaScript
					Minimize use of parser blocking resources via
						1. Deferring Javascript execution
						2. Using async attribute on <script>

			<Cmd Shft R> to do hard reload of page
			https://www.google.com/analytics/
